long.ar,bg,bn,ca,da,de,el,es,es_419,et,fa,fi,:
The best pictures of the best martial arts artist live today: Jackie Chan!

Features:
- daily awesome new image of Jackie!
- easy navigation between Google search and Apps, Bookmarks, Most Visited and Last Visited
-speed dial
- cool quote

Permissions explained:
- In order to display all bookmarks, apps and most/last visited sites, the extension needs to read those first. That's it :)

Feedback will be highly appreciated.
5* ratings will be my "juice" to move on and improve this cool extension.

Tired of Jackie Chan coolness? Uninstall it in a blink of an eye: go to chrome://extensions and deactivate the extension. 

Have fun! And follow your do!
